    "Ethical ConcernsThe integration of generative AI in language education is not without its ethical concerns.",
    "In this section, three possible ethical concerns are discussed.",
    "These concerns bring another perspective to ideas already covered in this article.",
    "Concern 1: Authentic authorshipThe arrival of generative AI has initiated transformative capabilities in content generation, ushering in a new educational landscape rich with potential yet fraught with complexities.",
    "One of these complexities is the increasingly indistinct line between creations by humans and those involving the creative use of AI, particularly within higher education."
